â˜• How Java Code is Executed (The Java Journey)

When you write a Java program, letâ€™s say:

Abhinav.java â€” this is your source code written in human-readable form.

ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’» Step 1: Compilation

You use the Java compiler (javac) to compile the source file:

